-18; " /><meta name="citation_reference" content="Wang L. X. ( 2019 ) ‘Global Drug Diffusion and Innovation with a Patent Pool: The Case of HIV Drug Cocktails’, SSRN, doi: 10.2139/ssrn.3426554. " /><meta name="citation_pdf_url" content="https://academic.oup.com/spp/article-pdf/47/5/733/37337391/scaa028.pdf" /><meta name="description" content="Abstract. The present document provides the take of innovation economists on the COVID-19 pandemic. It targets the general public and focuses on questions " /><meta name="citation_xml_url" content="https://academic.oup.com/spp/article-xml/47/5/733/5865508" />


