><div class="mixed-citation citation"><p class="mixed-citation-compatibility"><span class="person-group"><span class="name string-name"><div class="surname">Aristei</div> <div class="given-names">D.</div>
</span>, <span class="name string-name"><div class="surname">Sterlacchini</div> <div class="given-names">A.</div>
